parameters: \C[27][Rade]\C[0] You've been helping that girl all along, haven't you?
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Well, it's fine. Don't do anything unnecessary from now on.

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] That girl, did she break the chains of restraint? Her expression seemed
unusually bright. Not that it matters.

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Even so, what was that mysterious chain-like thing that occasionally appeared
on that girl? Not that it matters.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Forget about that. We're going to look for Regnus Grahardt.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] It's nothing. Forget about the girl.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] What was that girl's name again? I forgot.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] While you were away, I stopped by a village called Misa. I saw that girl there.
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] If it's that girl, she's alive. Not that it matters.

\C[27][Rade]\C[0] (Hmph... Did that girl break the chains of restraint? Her expression seemed
unusually bright. Not that it matters.)
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] Anyway, we're going to look for Regnus Grahardt.
Luca: Did you really see Luna-san?
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] I saw her. Are you doubting your master?
Luca: Yes. Because you always tell lies.
Luca: Aren't you a liar, Lady Rade?
\C[27][Rade]\C[0] I'm telling you I saw her~
